word_group.brief_definition: 犯罪；犯下罪行；实施犯罪
致力于；致力于此；使自己承担…

bilingual.source: The law will punish those who commit crimes.
bilingual.target: 法律会处分那些犯罪的人。

bilingual.source: He was accused of instigating others to commit a crime.
bilingual.target: 他被指控教唆他人犯罪。

bilingual.source: Trying to do something illegal or to commit an offence.
bilingual.target: 未遂罪,犯罪企图,试图做不合法的事或犯罪.

bilingual.source: He was spurred on by jealousy to commit a crime.
bilingual.target: 他受嫉妒心驱使而犯罪.
有些人因为蒙昧无知而犯罪.

bilingual.source: The gang commit three armed holdup on the same day.
bilingual.target: 犯罪团伙在同一天进行了三次武装抢劫.

bilingual.source: Are you sure you saw my client commit this crime?
bilingual.target: 你确定你看到我的当事人参与此次犯罪了吗？

bilingual.source: He is doing time for a crime he did not commit!
The mechanism of the crime lies in that the abettors not only commit a crime but also create perpetrators.
bilingual.target: 它的犯罪机理在于：教唆犯不仅制造了犯罪，还制造了犯罪人。

bilingual.source: Commit crime with the natural person in the system in our country penal code is opposite to unit crime.
bilingual.target: 在我国刑法体系中，与自然人犯罪相对应的是单位犯罪。

list.abstract: COMMIT命令用于把事务所做的修改保存到数据库，它把上一个COMMIT或ROLLBACK命令之后的全部事务都保存到数据库。
COMMIT，英语单词，及物动词，意为“犯罪，做错事；把...交托给；指派…作战；使…承担义务”。

yingyinNormal.en: Israel won't back us unless we commit troops.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有我们派兵，以色列才会支持我们。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe we could commit a crime, have them pick us up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许我们该犯个法，让他们来逮捕我们。

yingyinNormal.en: But here's a trick. You have to commit today to when you are going to submit each of the papers. And these deadlines that you commit to is binding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但有一点要注意今天你们就要决定好每篇论文你计划什么时候交。这些你选择的期限一经确定就不能更改。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no, no. Meet with him. Look, it doesn't commit us to anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不不，去见他，这并不能定下来什么。

yingyinNormal.en: I won't commit my people to a ground assault, just to pillage weapons.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能为了抢夺武器就让我的军队陷入地面战争。

yingyinNormal.en: I believe that this nation should commit itself, to achieving the goal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为我国应全力以赴，实现这一目标。

yingyinNormal.en: I won't commit our troops to fighting another ground war in Iraq, or in Syria.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我承诺不会让我们的部队再次参加伊拉克或叙利亚战争。

yingyinNormal.en: You know he's gonna commit that bomber straight to the Tree of Souls. Yeah, I know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是准备把炸弹投到灵魂树那里。我知道。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, well, excuse me for not wanting to live in a world where people can commit crimes without suffering the consequences. You are a criminal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗，原谅我不想活在这种人犯了罪，还不会受惩罚的地方你是个罪犯。

yingyinNormal.en: You'll have to commit to a vitamin and mineral regimen the rest of your life or risk things like anemia, osteoporosis diseases you would never think of.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在往后的生活中得服用维生素和矿物质否则很容易贫血，骨质疏松诸如此类你无法想象的疾病。

yingyinNormal.en: But as you are aware, sir, the employee handbook clearly states, and I quote, "No employee may, in part or in whole, commit the Krabby Patty secret formula to any recorded written or visual form, including memories, dreams, and or needlepoint."
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，老板，如你所知，员工手册上清楚写着“任何人不得以记忆、做梦、或是刺绣等方式将部分或全部蟹黄堡秘方转换为任何书面记录或是视觉形式。”
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: to be completely loyal to one person, organization, etc. or give all your time and effort to your work, an activity, etc.

examination_example.sentence: Employers have long seen the advantages of hiring school leavers who often prove themselves to be more <highlight>committed</highlight> and loyal employees than graduates.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 雇主们早就看到了雇佣离校生的好处，他们往往证明自己比毕业生更敬业、更忠诚。

examination_example.sentence: She uses outdated research to undermine the noble mission of organization <highlight>committed</highlight> to connecting children to a world beyond their own.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她利用过时的研究来破坏该组织致力将儿童与自己之外的世界联系起来的崇高使命。

sense_info_list.en: to promise sincerely that you will definitely do sth, keep to an agreement or arrangement, etc.

examination_example.sentence: We need them to imagine the United States as a place where they can be productive for a while without <highlight>committing</highlight> themselves to staying forever.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们需要他们把美国想象为一个他们可以暂时高效工作的地方，而无需承诺永久居留于此。

examination_example.sentence: Seymour made the change, went into his backyard, and expressed his displeasure by <highlight>committing</highlight> suicide.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Seymour对画作进行了调整之后，走进自家后院，以自杀的方式表达了他的不满。

sense_info_list.en: carry out or perpetrate (a mistake, crime, or immoral act)
to spend money or time on sth/sb
to order sb to be sent to a hospital, prison, etc.
sense_info_list.zh: 把某人送进(监狱或医院等)

examination_example.sentence: We are <highlight>committed</highlight> to fostering new music talent.

examination_example.sentence: It's just one of a growing number of businesses <highlight>committed</highlight> to slowly changing the way America farms.

examination_example.sentence: It is a popular belief that tech companies are <highlight>committed</highlight> to protecting their customers private data.
